title: #53 - Bella Poarch on Valkyrae Music Video Collab & Making the Most Viewed TikTok of 2020
itunes:title: #53 - Bella Poarch on Valkyrae Music Video Collab & Making the Most Viewed TikTok of 2020
description: After a 3rd place finish teaming up with Valkyrae during the Cash App Payday Uno Tournament, TikTok star and musical artist Bella Poarch makes her debut podcast appearance on a new episode of The CouRage and Nadeshot Show. Throughout the show she talks about her time in the Navy, what drew her to start making TikToks, as well as her reaction to having the most viewed TikTok in 2020.
